data.description: Very well-maintained and super-clean 4 bedroom all brick Cape Cod with many nice features: beautiful hardwood floors and crown molding. Many updates include new water heater, new fridge, new dishwasher, new faucet and ceramic sink, new LVP flooring in kitchen and new front & back storm door. All window treatments (new 2-inch faux wood) and leather couch are included. Entertain in your cozy rec room or manicured backyard. This home will not disappoint.
